The P贸voa de Varzim City Park (Parque da Cidade da P贸voa de Varzim) is an urban park of P贸voa de Varzim in Portugal.
The park is located in a former plain, where a small stream, farms and farmhouses existed. It includes landscaped hills, a lake, an island, and ways. The stream was recovered and wildlife started inhabiting the area. Small bridges, squares, and rustic buildings were built. The park includes the P贸voa de Varzim Municipal Stadium.
